Metadatat simply means data that describes data and 
html has a way it allows us to add metadata to our document.
the meta element is added to the head tag in our html file
and we have a couple of them.
For example the <meta charset="utf-8"> 
This specifies the character encoding scheme for this 
the project which is like the universal character set that
includes almost all the character for human language.
The meta element comes with some attributes we would see in the
the code in this project